Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as flowing water has no form,\Nand the breeze is invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,deductions take all shapes and styles\Nin each and every case to be solved
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's episode is the 1st in a series\Nof mind boggling mysteries
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll start with the adventures of\Nthese guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance\Nwith the I.Q. of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left\Nunsolved with Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not once but twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you,\Nbrave sir who has rescued me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Valiant nameless\Nknight dressed in black...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wish to grant me my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please remove that jet black\Nmask and show yourself to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! If that is what the princess wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will reveal my ugly scarred face to\Nyou beneath the light of this moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief! Come on dad! Be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's not too much time\Nleft before my school play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody can say these lines\Nwith a straight face, it's so unnatural!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who in the blazes wrote this syrupy\Nscript reading the script anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Sonoko! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she wrote the part for\Nthe black knight with Shinichi in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haha...that Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Knight and princess kiss passionately"\NThat's what it says right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh it's just pretend, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on Ran, who's going to do it?\NYou know, that knight's part...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why Conan, are you that curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph! I'll bet you got\Nsome goofy kid to do the part
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's somebody\Nyou both know VERY well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, you met him\Nduring one of your cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our school doctor, Dr. Araide
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the boys in our school\Nwere too embarrassed to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we asked Dr. Araide when he\Ncame by to give us our physical exams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he played a lot of leads\Nin school plays in his days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why he's so good at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he says the lines well and\Nhe knows how to handle women...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no way! I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no! Don't do it, Ran
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.\NHe's just overlooking our rehearsals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's going to dress like a man\Nto play the part of the knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got practice in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to take a bath and\Nget to sleep right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, the bath's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks, I wanted to take a bath too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you two\Ngo to the public bath
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's closed today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go ask Dr. Agasa\Nto let us use his bath then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going there tonight anyway to talk\Nabout our camping trip this weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get my{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to\Ntrouble the man too much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so take your baths together and\Ncome home right away, you hear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You..you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've go be kidding!\NWhy do I have to bathe with Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh dear....\NI meant to say, it wouldn't be proper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:42.39,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,PERIOUS RETURN-\NDETECTIVES IN THE CAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's strange
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately, Ran's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something in Ran's eyes and\Nthe way she treats me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it isn't way a person\Ntreats a 7 year old, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it could just be\Nmy imagination I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who you really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have something to do in the basement,\Nit'll take me until morning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't disturb me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what if Ai is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she was suspicious,\Nwhy wouldn't she ask me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the way Ran is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where is Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, Ai's in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran\Ndon't go down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you say hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright Doctor.\NI shouldn't bother her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you later Ai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm running away?...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the new century!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Doc, about our conversation\Nthe other day regarding Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you make a handy robot\Njust in case of an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...what kind did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something that moves and sounds\Nexactly me. My double so to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I could make something like that,\NI'd already be a millionaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, the tent's up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't forget the tent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai and I will build stove so why don't you\Nkids go get some wood for the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight we're going to have\Nbarbeque, a barbeque...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!\NI think we've got enough, let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey guys! Come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found something interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a limestone cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sign says "Do Not Enter-Danger"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words on this is\Nwhat caught my attention
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow the dragon's path...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a glow of supreme bliss\Nwill shine on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glow of supreme bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A glow that makes you very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haha, here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The catch is this big [to]\Ncarved in the stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokujo Unaju
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Topaz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonneru (tunnel)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokugawa buried treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just kidding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, comeback here guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nwe're just going to check it out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh for goodness sakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sure is a huge cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a limestone cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd be so big inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The filter's still damp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if someone\Nbesides us is in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's keeping them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably exploring the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, their leader's\Na very curious detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind them!\NGive me hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!!? Look at that, it's a light
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's over there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the person who was smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody's already\Nfound the treasure before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw rats! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn it all,\Nwe should've come in here earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the treasure would've been ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Genta??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A b..bo..a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kids, some kids saw us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief,\Nyou think their parents are with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was only the 4 kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! What a run of bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First we rob a bank\Nbut 1 of us gets our face seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we had to kill him and we figured
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if we buried him in here,\Nnobody'd find out who we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but now those kids saw us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,now those kids saw us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! Where'd they go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're we going to do\Nwhen we find those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only logical thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to put them\Nto eternal sleep here in this dark tomb
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By blowing a hole\Nthrough their little heads
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get to the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him and I will search\Naround here a little longer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Haibara!\NCan you hear me? Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara! Answer me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me if you can hear me, Haibara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...Haibara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this, I don't believe\Nyou've been cooking your own meals
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the switch is off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll go tell those guys\Nthat we didn't see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan will think of a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co, Conan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh, what's the matter?\NWhy're you bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean, the bullet he shot, hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan,\Nwe've got to get out of here right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before those bad men come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W, wait...Ai and the Professor are\Nout there waiting for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sooner or later,\Nthey'll come in this cave to look for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they come in\Nnot knowing what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,chances are, those bad men will kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to warn that\Nthis cave is dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...how're we going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we write a note and those bad guys\Nfind it, they'll just rip it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll just have to\Nkeep going deeper inside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and keep trying to reach them\Nwith the badge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we go in any deeper,\Nthe radio waves won't reach that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what're we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to use these transmitters,\Nthe ones we use to track criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a seal on the back,\Nwe can peel back about 10...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, but...\Nwhat're we going to use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do what I tell you,\Nnow hurry, take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats! Where'd those kids go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't look like they made it\Nto the entrance or to the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...\Nand we already searched around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only place we haven't looked is\Nthe way that goes deeper in the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph! That saves us\Nthe trouble of going after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those kids are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear\Nthe inside of this cave is a giant maze,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a lot of people have died\Nwithout ever finding their way out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're going to go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got take care of all loose ends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks like\Nthose kids did head inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eye glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those could be from somebody else\Nwho got lost in here though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood! It's blood!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha! And it's still damp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, that means we'll catch up\Nto those kids in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh, that's right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they're TOO late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go look in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fine...\Nnow that I put a huge bandage on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way Genta...\Ncan't you walk any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those guys'll catch up to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd hurt if I rocked you too much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't come inside and\Nsaid it wouldn't hurt to check it out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan wouldn't have gotten hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started it, I shouldn't found\Nthis cave in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dummy! You know it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got carried away and happened to see\Nthose guys with the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you are wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't come inside this cave,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a murder would've gone unsolved. But\Nthanks to you, we know who the killers are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...as soon as\Nwe get away from those guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we've got a barbeque to cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's be optimistic about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Everybody come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It splits into 2 here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh, what'll we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's "janken to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ge...Genta...\Nhand me the wristwatch light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey kids, where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey kids, where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! It's wood for the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4 piles stacked neatly in front of the cave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...\NI don't believe it...those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are inside this cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this, the road splits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn! Which way'd they go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's a wristwatch with a light,\Nthose kids have fancy stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we're on the right track,\Nthose kids went this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trap!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may be only kids
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but do you think they wouldn't notice\Nif they dropped something with a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they were thoughtful enough\Nto tuck the belt away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They made it look like they went this way\Nbut actually, they went that way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those kids think they're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting curious, I can't wait to see\Nwhat those kids look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Their faces full of fear,\Nbegging for their life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, deliberately leaving the watch\Nshowing them we came this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes..I'm sure\Nthose guys are going the other way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those men robbed a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's\Nat least 1 smart guy among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what happens if they split in 2 groups\Nand come this way too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph, it won't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they can't even use\Na transmitter in this cave,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they know it could cost them\Ntheir life if they split up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, a fish!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...does that fish have eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes it does, I can see it!\NI think it's a sweetfish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What was that??\NAre we going to eat it??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No you silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not running away\Nwithout thinking up a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fish that live in caves have no eyes,\Nif this fish has eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's a good{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce\Nit swam in here from some river
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that if we move upstream\Nthis underground river...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll find a way out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are Kudo's aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they must have gotten\Nlost in here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why'd he leave them here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is terrible,\Nwe've got to find them right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's on the ground\Naround here a lot of them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why these are\Nthe button shaped transmitters!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they form a shape
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me reduce the transmission area...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why this is!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,110, emergency!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What is this!! It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn those kids!!\NThey pulled one on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's head back and find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't possibly\Nget out through there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fish does seem to\Ncome from here though...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean\Nwe'll never get out alive??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too early to give up hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the roots of a tree are growing\Nthrough the roof of the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we're right under\Nthe surface of the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the way out is probably very close by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any way to get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an egg!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something like a giant egg here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's just an egg shaped rock\Non top of another rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh shucks, what a bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've come to a very strange place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the path splits into 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder which one leads to the way out..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...it isn't natural for a rock\Nlike that to rest on another rock
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone put it there deliberately...\Nbut for what reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that! Something's carved on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those lost in the darkness,\Nfollow the dragon's path
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a glow of supreme bliss\Nwill shine upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those lost in the darkness?...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost the same words we found\Non the stone monument we found outside
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no\NYikes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it, it's those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're close by!! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move! Just keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bats that live in caves eat bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why they respond to\Nslight movements and sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy Ayumi,\Ndon't go finding anymore weird things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're lucky you did
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bats that live in caves nest no more\Nthan 300 meters from the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the way out is very close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our problem is, we don't know which\None of tunnels leads to the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is right,\Nthe dragon's path will show us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats, my eyes are getting fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to the puzzle is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the huge [to] carved on the stone in front\Nof the cave and the words "dragon's path"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the egg shaped rock\Non top of the other rock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,[to]...[dragon's path]...[egg]...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's try each of the tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N, no...we're only going to go into 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words "Those lost in the darkness"\Nrefers to those lost in the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"glow of supreme bliss means\Nthe light of the way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th, that means...the carvings on the stone\Nin front of the cave and on that rock are
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hints as how to get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dragon's path that leads out is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th...that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eek, he's bleeding so badly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Footsteps!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, those guys are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh,. What're we going to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no...they're coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're idiots\NI've already read your gameplan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the same blood type as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.84,0:24:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you do know...about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:29.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,PERILOUS RETURN-\NTHE WOUNDED DETECTIVE
